name: Main motor speed
description: The speed to set on the main motor, from 0 to 100

name: Vibrator speed
description: The speed to set on the vibrator motor, from 0 to 100

name: Minimum value
description: The minimum value of the range speed to randomly set on the main motor, from 0 to 100

name: Maximum value
description: The maximum value of the range speed to randomly set on the main motor, from 0 to 100

name: Minimum value
description: The minimum value of the range speed to randomly set on the vibrator motor, from 0 to 100

name: Maximum value
description: The maximum value of the range speed to randomly set on the vibrator motor, from 0 to 100

name: Starting speed
description: The starting speed to apply to the main motor, from 0 to 100

name: Ending speed
description: The final speed to reach on the main motor, from 0 to 100

name: Ramp time
description: The time to transition from minimum to maximum speed on the main motor

name: Starting speed
description: The starting speed to apply to the vibrator motor, from 0 to 100

name: Ending speed
description: The final speed to reach on the vibrator motor, from 0 to 100

name: Ramp time
description: The time to transition from minimum to maximum speed on the vibrator motor

name: Minimum value
description: The minimum amount of time to wait (in milliseconds)

name: Maximum value
description: The maximum amount of time to wait (in milliseconds)

name: Step number
description: The number of the step to jump to
